cat << EOF
THC-RUT (aRe yoU There, pronouced as root) is your first knife on foreign
network.

It gathers informations from local and remote networks. It offers a wide range
of network discovery tools: arp lookup on an IP range, spoofed DHCP request,
RARP, BOOTP, ICMP-ping, ICMP address mask request, OS fingerprintings,
high-speed host discovery, ...  The tool is capable of discovering a Class B
network within 10 minutes.
EOF
